com.navis.framework.presentation.charting.jfree

Class CarinaChartFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.navis.framework.presentation.charting.jfree.CarinaChartFactory

  • public class CarinaChartFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class does NOT extend JFree ChartFactory, due to having only static methods which we would like to override. This class is to be used as a Singleton.
    Author:
    Gisella Saavedra, May 16, 2011

      • createGaugeChart

        public org.jfree.chart.JFreeChart createGaugeChart(GaugeChart.TypeEnum inGaugeType,
                                                   @Nullable
                                                   java.lang.String inTitle,
                                                   @Nullable
                                                   java.lang.String inValueAnnotation,
                                                   org.jfree.data.general.ValueDataset inValueDataset,
                                                   boolean inLegend)
        Create a Gauge chart depending on inGaugeType. Tooltips not implemented for JFree DialPlot (no renderers).
        Parameters:
        inGaugeType - gauge type: ARC or METER
        inTitle - chart title if any
        inValueAnnotation - value annotation if any. For example, "units" for the value.
        inValueDataset - value dataset
        inLegend - true if legend desired
        Returns:
        a gauge chart suing ArcDialFrame for ARC and StandardDialFrame for METER.
